title: Bloomberg Markets: MongoDB CEO on First Day of Trading
itunes:title: Bloomberg Markets: MongoDB CEO on First Day of Trading
description:
Bloomberg Markets with Carol Massar and Cory Johnson.\u0010\u0010GUESTS:\u0010Dev C Ittycheria\u0010President/CEO\u0010MongoDB \u0010Discussing the first database company to go public in more than 20 years and the business of software for developers. \u0010\u0010Michael Sheldon\u0010Chief Investment Officer\u0010RDM Financial Group\u0010Discussing whether value is going to outperform growth on a more sustained basis.
